Parliament, Monday, 15 July 2019 – The Select Committee on Health and Social Services will tomorrow be briefed by the Department of Social Development on its strategic plan and budget vote. Details of the meeting: Date: 16 July 2019
	Time: 10:00 – 12:30
	Venue: Committee Room V226, Second Floor, Old Assembly Building Meanwhile, the Select Committee on Land Reform, Environment, Mineral Resources and Energy will be briefed by the Department of Energy on its annual performance plan for 2019/20 and budget vote. Details of the meeting: Date 16 July 2019
	Time: 10:00 – 13:00
	Venue: Committee Room V475, Fourth Floor, Old Assembly Building ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the committee’s Media Officer: Name: Ms Yoliswa Landu 
